-- Capital One sees 2008 writedowns of about $4.9 bln
-- 
-- Thu Oct 18, 2007 5:45pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/10/18/us-capitalone-results-chargeoffs-idUSWEN177520071018

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Capital One Financial Corp ( COF.N ). expects to write off about $4.9 billion of loans in 2008, the company's chief executive said on a conference call on Thursday. 

 CEO Richard Fairbank said Capital One would likely write down $1.2 billion of loans in the fourth quarter. (Reporting by  Dan Wilchins )